<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416000' id='t-416000'>If I were here playing cello, or playing on a synth, or sharing my music with you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='419000' id='t-419000'>I'd be able to show things about myself that I can't tell you in words,</span>
