<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='427000' id='t-427000'>I think that's true for many of us, and I want to give you two examples</span>
