<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='433000' id='t-433000'>from ourselves to the outside world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435000' id='t-435000'>The first is a really crazy project that we're building right now, called</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='439000' id='t-439000'>Death and the Powers. And it's a big opera,</span>
