<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445000' id='t-445000'>And it's about a man, rich, successful, powerful, who wants to live forever.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='450000' id='t-450000'>So, he figures out a way to download himself into his environment,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='452000' id='t-452000'>actually into a series of books.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='455000' id='t-455000'>So this guy wants to live forever, he downloads himself into his environment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='458000' id='t-458000'>The main singer disappears at the beginning of the opera</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='462000' id='t-462000'>and the entire stage becomes the main character. It becomes his legacy.</span>
