<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534000' id='t-534000'>The largest set piece in the opera is called The System. It's a series of books.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='538000' id='t-538000'>Every single book is robotic, so they all move, they all make sound,</span>
